{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1076327_translations":{"at":1772689420766,"data":{"id":1076327,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jonathan Kos-Read (born 1973), also known as Cao Cao (Chinese: 曹操; pinyin: Cáo Cāo), is an American film and television actor based in the People's Republic of China. While well known in China, his work is little-known in the United States. Kos-Read uses the stage name Cao Cao, which is also the name of the penultimate chancellor of the Eastern Han Dynasty, a historical figure well-known to most Chinese people.","name":"Jonathan Kos-Read","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"曹操（1973年—），原名乔纳森·科斯-瑞德（英语：Jonathan Kos-Read），出生于美国，演艺事业主要在中国的演员。“曹操”这个名字来源于三国历史人物曹操。作为一个能流利讲带点北京腔普通话的白种人，曹操所饰演的角色大多是古代的外国人，是中国观众最眼熟的外籍演员之一。他已经出演过100多部影视剧包括《走向共和》、《寻龙诀》和《狙击手》等","name":"曹操","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"曹操","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"曹操（1973 年—），原名喬納森·科斯 - 瑞德（英語：Jonathan Kos - Read），出生於美國，演藝事業主要在中國的演員。“曹操”這個名字來源於三國歷史人物曹操。作為一個能流利講帶點北京腔普通話的白種人，曹操所飾演的角色大多是古代的外國人，是中國觀眾最眼熟的外籍演員之一。他已經出演過 100 多部影視劇包括《走向共和》、《鬼吹燈之尋龍訣》和《狙擊手》等","name":"曹操","primary":false}}]}},"person_4511313_translations":{"at":1772689425175,"data":{"id":4511313,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"\"Thongfah\" Alicha Sripratak is a model, actor and student at Chulalongkorn University. After graduating from Triam Udom Suksa School, she began studying in the business program but transferred to communication arts after starting her acting career.","name":"Alicha Sriprathak","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","na